        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <actionDate>2017-03-10</actionDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-10-06T13:56:08Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Fair Treatment for Families of Veterans Act</strong></p> <p>This bill changes the effective date for reductions or discontinuances of Department of Veterans Affairs dependency and indemnity compensation by reason of the death of a payee from the last day of the month before death to the last day of the month of death.</p> <p> A veteran's surviving spouse who receives both dependency/indemnity compensation and service- or non-service-connected disability/death payments for the month of the veteran's death shall be entitled to the greater of the two payments. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-03-10T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
